<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Failed</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #fff4f4;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .container h1 {
            color: #d9534f;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .container p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #d9534f;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: shake 0.5s;
            animation-iteration-count: 2;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #d9534f;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(217, 83, 79, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #c9302c;
        }
        .footer-note {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Animation */
        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25%, 75% { transform: translateX(-5px); }
            50% { transform: translateX(5px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">‚ùå</div>
        <h1>Transaction Failed</h1>
        <p>Unfortunately, your transaction could not be processed. Please check your payment details and try again.</p>
        <p>If the problem persists, contact our support team for assistance.</p>
        <a href="/" class="button">Return to Home</a>
        <p class="footer-note">Need help? <a href="mailto:support@example.com">Contact support</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
